sections.markdown:
# ArgoCD Analytics based on Logs emitted by ArgoCD components
ArgoCD has several components: server, notification-server, 

Use Cases
- Auditing who triggered Syncs
- Identify Sync Spikes, issues with Syncs ...

sections.title: All Logs from ArgoCD Notifications Controller

input.value:
fetch logs
| filter contains(k8s.container.name, "argocd-notifications-controller")
| parse content, """'time="' ISO8601:argotimestamp '"' LD 'level=' LD:level ' msg="' LD:msg '" resource=' LD:resource"""
| makeTimeseries count(), by:{resource}

grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch logs
| filter contains(k8s.container.name, "argocd-notifications-controller")
| parse content, """'time="' ISO8601:argotimestamp '"' LD 'level=' LD:level ' msg="' LD:msg '" resource=' LD:resource"""
| makeTimeseries by:{resource}, count()
grail.query:
